|}

=== Initial Value Decoding ===

The initial value is assembled from bit 7 of each byte using ROR (rotate right):
# For each byte, ASL A puts bit 7 into carry
# ROR into result byte rotates carry into bit 7
# After 5 bytes, 3 LSR operations shift right 3 positions

Result range: 0-31

=== Rate Index Decoding ===

Rate index = (byte0 AND $60) >> 3

This extracts bits 6-5 and shifts them to become the starting index into the growth rate table.

